												<div class="description author withsidebar">
													<h6><a href="https://lithub.com/author/josh-cook/">Josh Cook</a></h6>
													Josh Cook is is a bookseller at Porter Square Books in Cambridge, Massachusetts, where he has worked since 2004. He is also author of the critically acclaimed postmodern detective novel <em>An Exaggerated Murder</em> and his fiction, criticism, and poetry have appeared in numerous leading literary publications. He grew up in Lewiston, Maine and lives in Somerville, MA.																									</div>
